name: Garlic Chicken
steps: Heat oil in pan|Add garlic and onions|Saute till golden|Add tomatoes|Cook till soft|Add chicken pieces|Cook on medium-high|Season with salt and pepper|Garnish with cilantro|Serve hot

name: Tomato Soup
steps: Heat oil|Add onion and garlic|Add tomatoes and water|Boil|Blend and serve
